name: RTCInboundRtpStreamStats.qpSum
description: The qpSum property of the RTCInboundRtpStreamStats dictionary is a value generated by adding the Quantization Parameter (QP) values for every frame sent or received to date on the video track corresponding to this RTCInboundRtpStreamStats object.
